# Font:
Playfair italic (header)
Montserrant light italic (body)
Baskerville itallic (paragraph)

# Vision:
No excuse to not learn korean

# Mission:
Make it simple, and provide plenty for all korean learners 

# Negative Mission:
Make it fun, make it interesting, make specific learning (specific is different from customizable)

# Colour palatte:
#f4e4e1 (Soft Pink) → rgb(244, 228, 225) -> background
#f0edd8 (Light Beige) → rgb(240, 237, 216) -> secondary background
#d8f0f0 (Pale Cyan) → rgb(216, 240, 240) -> accent colour
#3b3838 (Charcoal Gray) → rgb(59, 56, 56) -> text
#ffffff (White) → rgb(255, 255, 255) -> accent colour 
